 temperature trends (1995) Science, 270, pp. 780-783; Wu, Z.E., Schneider, K., Hu, Z.-Z., Cao, L., The impact of global warming on ENSO in climate records (2001) COLA Rep 110, Center for Ocean-Land-Atmosphere Studies, p. 22. , [Available from the Center for Ocean-Land-Atmosphere Studies 4041 Powder Mill Road Suite 302 Calverton MD 20705.]; Wunsch, C., The interpretation of short climate records with comments on the North Atlantic and Southern Oscillations (1999) Bull. Am. Meteorol. Soc., 80, pp. 245-255; Zorita, E., González-Rouco, F., Disagreement between predictions of the future behavior of the Arctic Oscillation as simulated in two different climate models: Implications of global warming (2000) Geophys. Res. Lett., 27, pp. 1755-1758","Hu, Z.-Z.; Ctr.for Ocean-Land-Atmosphere Studs., 4041 Powder Mill Rd., Calverton, MD 20705, United States; email: hu@cola.iges.org",,,,,,,,02806495,,,,"English","Tellus Ser. A Dyn. Meteorol. Oceanogr.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-1642447122
